body:
I mainly listen to EDM. My favorites are Dubstep, Drum & Bass, and Electro House, but I'll honestly listen to any EDM genre, including Glitch Hop, all kinds of House, Trance, Chill, Moombahcore, Hardcore, Hardstyle, Trap, etc. etc. etc.
I also enjoy Jazz, Gospel, Classical, and to some extent, Rock.

I hate most pop, interestingly enough. Don't know why. Rap is meh. Country isn't bad but isn't good either.
What music do you listen to? c:
